Loving this new hair mask that I tried from @mysticnaturals 🙀
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I just tried this hair mask from @mysticnaturals 
sent by the brand itself #prpackage
This is their kerela coconut butter and moringa hair mask
This has coconut butter, avocado butter, mowrah butter, mango butter, moringa oil, licorice & hibiscus extract, amla & bhringraj extract, silk protein and wheat germ oil

priced at Rs. 595/- for 70gm 
will last you really long depending on your hair length. So a little goes a long way😉

what it claims
repairs dry & damaged hair, reduces hair fall and prevents pre mature grey hair. Helps in calming scalp itchiness and controls dandruff.

My first impression
My hair feels so so soft as you can see here♥️. It gave me a hair fall more than usual in the first wash, could be because my hair needs to adjust to certain product but my dry and dull hair really feels good after using this. Let's see if this one actually reduces my hairfall. So stay tuned for more updates on this.🐷
